text: Sten Elliot (born 24 December 1925) is a Swedish former sailor who competed in the 1960 Summer Olympics. He was born in Göteborg, Sweden. ==References== Category:1925 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish male sailors (sport) Category:Olympic sailors of Sweden Category:Sailors at the 1960 Summer Olympics – Dragon Category:Sportspeople from Gothenburg
